花、双手搬运物料等等。 但机器人的这些能力并没有打动业内专家。 美国电机电子工程师学会（IEEE）的一篇评论员文章直言，特斯拉未能通过其新的人形机器人原型机展示任何独特和令人印象深刻的东西。 擎天柱首秀后，专家质疑重重，他们是怎么说的？ | 每经网特斯拉人形机器人擎天柱原型机正式亮相，预计售价不到 2 万美元，未来产量可达数百万台，有哪些技术亮点？如何评价 9 月 30 号特斯拉举办的 2022 AI Day ? 有哪些亮点和槽点？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-7699bdb4efba59895d4c3a47bf027bef_b.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "17 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/557431840"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IqOi74vLJlaVtEAMaCDg2MTU2NTcyIKLT5pkGMAQ4UkAfcgk1NTc0MzE4NDB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "32_1664810075.3732111", "card_id": "Q_355912099", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 49}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你在面试时，遇到的最奇葩最想吐槽的面试官是什么样的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-819d8f66d62315a0bfc40328663588ae_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "17 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/355912099"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IqOi74vLJlaVtEAMaCDQxMzY5Mjk5IMqStu4FMAE4a0AgcgkzNTU5MTIwOTl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "33_1664810075.37385", "card_id": "Q_290236443", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 44}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "采购的日常工作是怎样的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "可以从通常的汇报对象是谁？衡量工作的重要指标是什么？岗位所服务的对象是谁？这几个方面来聊"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-fae53caa11cfa8ec6be79415fe637b96.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "16 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/290236443"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IqOi74vLJlaVtEAMaCDI2